data.description: Cedar Hill ALL BRICK home on private 5 ACRES- is move-in ready and available immediately! This immaculate ranch home features 3 large bedrooms, all with large walk-in closets, 6 panel doors and ceiling fans. The Master suite boasts a huge master closet and a super luxurious master bathroom-complete with a walk-in shower and large soaking tub. The kitchen has loads of cabinet space and is open to the wood-floored eat-in kitchen- that is bright and airy, and looks out onto the private patio. The spacious main floor laundry room doubles as a mud room. The Oversized garage has plenty of room for cars or a workshop, and has a separate entrance door to the patio. Outside you will find that the covered front porch will be the perfect spot for enjoying the fall sunsets upon your large unspoiled view of the land. Suitable for horses, lots of room for a barn or outbuilding! Your dream home awaits you!
